=\"corner corner-tr\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-bl\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-br\"></div>\n         <div class=\"media-showcase-inner\">\n           <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class=\"asset-media-contain\">\n             <source src=\"asset://1774738684886\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n           </video>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"project-details fade-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container split-layout\">\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Challenge</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Traditional healthcare event announcements often suffer from visual clutter and safe, sterile design choices. The goal was to break through the noise of corporate feeds with a structure that felt authoritative yet distinctly modern, stripped of unnecessary polish.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Imperfection</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Embracing a brutalist grid, the typography acts as the primary structural element. Instead of hiding the framework, the design exposes it. Harsh contrasts, unadorned borders, and strict monochrome application ensure the message is delivered with absolute clarity and industrial weight.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"next-project-nav mt-4\">\n    <div class=\"container text-center\">\n      <p class=\"label\">[CONTINUE]</p>\n      <a href=\"work.html\" class=\"mega-title hover-accent\">Next Project <svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7\"/></svg></a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</main>\n\n<footer class=\"site-footer\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"footer-grid\">\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">MULTIMEDIA DESIGNER</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Embracing imperfection.<br>Finding beauty in the raw.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">NAVIGATION</h4>\n        <ul class=\"footer-links\">\n          <li><a href=\"index.html\">Home</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"work.html\">Work</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"about.html\">About</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"contact.html\">Contact</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">CONNECT</h4>\n        <ul class=\"footer-links\">\n          <li><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/amielnavigar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LinkedIn</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"footer-bottom\">\n      <div class=\"copyright\">© 2026</div>\n      <div class=\"quote\">Nothing is permanent.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</footer>\n\n<div id=\"custom-cursor\" class=\"custom-cursor\"></div>\n<script src=\"script.js\"></script>"},{"name":"project-veega.html","html":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"style.css\">\n<div class=\"page-transition\"></div>\n<header id=\"main-header\">\n  <div class=\"container header-inner\">\n    <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"logo\">AMIEL NAVIGAR</a>\n    <nav>\n      <ul class=\"nav-links\">\n        <li><a href=\"index.html\">HOME</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"work.html\" class=\"active\">WORK</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"about.html\">ABOUT</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"contact.html\">CONTACT</a></li>\n        <li>\n          <button id=\"theme-toggle\" class=\"theme-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Theme\">\n            <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M12 2v20a10 10 0 1 0 0-20z\"/></svg>\n          </button>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </nav>\n  </div>\n</header>\n\n<main class=\"page-project\">\n  <section class=\"project-hero fade-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <a href=\"work.html\" class=\"link-btn mb-4\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path d=\"M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7\"/></svg> BACK TO WORK</a>\n      \n      <div class=\"label\">[CASE STUDY]</div>\n      <h1 class=\"mega-title\">Veega Instagram<br>Ad</h1>\n      \n      <div class=\"project-meta mt-3\">\n        <div class=\"meta-item\">\n          <span class=\"label\">CLIENT</span>\n          <p>Veega</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"meta-item\">\n          <span class=\"label\">ROLE</span>\n          <p>Animation</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"meta-item\">\n          <span class=\"label\">YEAR</span>\n          <p>2023</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"project-media fade-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"media-showcase\" style=\"cursor: default;\">\n         <div class=\"corner corner-tl\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-tr\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-bl\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-br\"></div>\n         <div class=\"media-showcase-inner\">\n           <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class=\"asset-media-contain\">\n             <source src=\"asset://1774738660376\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n           </video>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"project-details fade-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container split-layout\">\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Challenge</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Creating a dynamic and engaging animation for an Instagram advertisement to capture user attention instantly. The piece had to balance brand identity with smooth, eye-catching motion within a fast-paced environment.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Execution</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Leveraging bold typography and kinetic movements, the animation embraces a rhythmic and energetic visual language. The structure keeps the viewer focused on key messages while maintaining an engaging loop suited for social media.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"next-project-nav mt-4\">\n    <div class=\"container text-center\">\n      <p class=\"label\">[CONTINUE]</p>\n      <a href=\"work.html\" class=\"mega-title hover-accent\">Next Project <svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7\"/></svg></a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</main>\n\n<footer class=\"site-footer\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"footer-grid\">\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">MULTIMEDIA DESIGNER</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Embracing imperfection.<br>Finding beauty in the raw.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">NAVIGATION</h4>\n        <ul class=\"footer-links\">\n          <li><a href=\"index.html\">Home</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"work.html\">Work</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"about.html\">About</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"contact.html\">Contact</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">CONNECT</h4>\n        <ul class=\"footer-links\">\n          <li><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/amielnavigar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LinkedIn</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"footer-bottom\">\n      <div class=\"copyright\">© 2026</div>\n      <div class=\"quote\">Nothing is permanent.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</footer>\n\n<div id=\"custom-cursor\" class=\"custom-cursor\"></div>\n<script src=\"script.js\"></script>"},{"name":"project-pf-chicken.html","html":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"style.css\">\n<div class=\"page-transition\"></div>\n<header id=\"main-header\">\n  <div class=\"container header-inner\">\n    <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"logo\">AMIEL NAVIGAR</a>\n    <nav>\n      <ul class=\"nav-links\">\n        <li><a href=\"index.html\">HOME</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"work.html\" class=\"active\">WORK</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"about.html\">ABOUT</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"contact.html\">CONTACT</a></li>\n        <li>\n          <button id=\"theme-toggle\" class=\"theme-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Theme\">\n            <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M12 2v20a10 10 0 1 0 0-20z\"/></svg>\n          </button>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </nav>\n  </div>\n</header>\n\n<main class=\"page-project\">\n  <section class=\"project-hero fade-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <a href=\"work.html\" class=\"link-btn mb-4\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path d=\"M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7\"/></svg> BACK TO WORK</a>\n      \n      <div class=\"label\">[CASE STUDY]</div>\n      <h1 class=\"mega-title\">PF Fried Chicken<br>Father's Day</h1>\n      \n      <div class=\"project-meta mt-3\">\n        <div class=\"meta-item\">\n          <span class=\"label\">CLIENT</span>\n          <p>Purefoods</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"meta-item\">\n          <span class=\"label\">ROLE</span>\n          <p>Graphic Design</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"meta-item\">\n          <span class=\"label\">YEAR</span>\n          <p>2023</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"project-media fade-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"media-showcase\" style=\"cursor: default;\">\n         <div class=\"corner corner-tl\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-tr\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-bl\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-br\"></div>\n         <div class=\"media-showcase-inner\">\n           <img src=\"asset://1774739075614\" alt=\"PF Crispy Fried Chicken Ads Father's Day\" class=\"asset-media-contain\" referrerPolicy=\"no-referrer\">\n         </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"project-details fade-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container split-layout\">\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Challenge</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Stripping away the excess to reveal the core message within a crowded digital landscape. The objective was to prioritize raw function over decorative polish to capture attention quickly and cleanly on social feeds.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Execution</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Utilizing stark contrasts and unyielding grids to frame the asset. Imperfections in texture are embraced, allowing the inherent visual qualities of the media to speak for themselves, unfiltered and honest.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"next-project-nav mt-4\">\n    <div class=\"container text-center\">\n      <p class=\"label\">[CONTINUE]</p>\n      <a href=\"work.html\" class=\"mega-title hover-accent\">Next Project <svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7\"/></svg></a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</main>\n\n<footer class=\"site-footer\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"footer-grid\">\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">MULTIMEDIA DESIGNER</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Embracing imperfection.<br>Finding beauty in the raw.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">NAVIGATION</h4>\n        <ul class=\"footer-links\">\n          <li><a href=\"index.html\">Home</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"work.html\">Work</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"about.html\">About</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"contact.html\">Contact</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer-col\">\n        <h4 class=\"footer-heading\">CONNECT</h4>\n        <ul class=\"footer-links\">\n          <li><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/amielnavigar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LinkedIn</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"footer-bottom\">\n      <div class=\"copyright\">© 2026</div>\n      <div class=\"quote\">Nothing is permanent.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</footer>\n\n<div id=\"custom-cursor\" class=\"custom-cursor\"></div>\n<script src=\"script.js\"></script>"},{"name":"project-courts.html","html":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"style.css\">\n<div class=\"page-transition\"></div>\n<header id=\"main-header\">\n  <div class=\"container header-inner\">\n    <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"logo\">AMIEL NAVIGAR</a>\n    <nav>\n      <ul class=\"nav-links\">\n        <li><a href=\"index.html\">HOME</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"work.html\" class=\"active\">WORK</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"about.html\">ABOUT</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"contact.html\">CONTACT</a></li>\n        <li>\n          <button id=\"theme-toggle\" class=\"theme-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Theme\">\n            <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M12 2v20a10 10 0 1 0 0-20z\"/></svg>\n          </button>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </nav>\n  </div>\n</header>\n\n<main class=\"page-project\">\n  <section class=\"project-hero fade-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <a href=\"work.html\" class=\"link-btn mb-4\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path d=\"M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7\"/></svg> BACK TO WORK</a>\n      \n      <div class=\"label\">[CASE STUDY]</div>\n      <h1 class=\"mega-title\">Courts Father's<br>Day Post</h1>\n      \n      <div class=\"project-meta mt-3\">\n        <div class=\"meta-item\">\n          <span class=\"label\">CLIENT</span>\n          <p>Courts</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"meta-item\">\n          <span class=\"label\">ROLE</span>\n          <p>Graphic Design</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"meta-item\">\n          <span class=\"label\">YEAR</span>\n          <p>2023</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"project-media fade-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"media-showcase\" style=\"cursor: default;\">\n         <div class=\"corner corner-tl\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-tr\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-bl\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-br\"></div>\n         <div class=\"media-showcase-inner\">\n           <img src=\"asset://1774739118170\" alt=\"Courts Father's Day Socmed Post\" class=\"asset-media-contain\" referrerPolicy=\"no-referrer\">\n         </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"project-details fade-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container split-layout\">\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Challenge</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Stripping away the excess to reveal the core message within a crowded digital landscape. The objective was to prioritize raw function over decorative polish to capture attention quickly and cleanly on social feeds.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Execution</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Utilizing stark contrasts and unyielding grids to frame the asset. Imperfections in texture are embraced, allowing the inherent visual qualities of the media to speak for themselves, unfiltered and honest.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"next-project-nav mt-4\">\n    <div class=\"container text-center\">\n      <p class=\"label\">[CONTINUE]</p>\n      <a href=\"wor