>\n          <p>Purefoods</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"meta-item\">\n          <span class=\"label\">ROLE</span>\n          <p>Motion Graphics</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"meta-item\">\n          <span class=\"label\">YEAR</span>\n          <p>2023</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"project-media fade-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"media-showcase\" style=\"cursor: default;\">\n         <div class=\"corner corner-tl\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-tr\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-bl\"></div><div class=\"corner corner-br\"></div>\n         <div class=\"media-showcase-inner\">\n           <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class=\"asset-media-contain\">\n             <source src=\"asset://1774739380098\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n           </video>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"project-details fade-in-up\">\n    <div class=\"container split-layout\">\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Challenge</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Creating a dynamic and engaging animation for a digital advertisement to capture user attention instantly. The piece had to balance brand identity with smooth, eye-catching motion within a fast-paced environment.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"split-text\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">The Execution</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-muted\">Leveraging bold typography and kinetic movements, the animation embraces a rhythmic and energetic visual language. The structure keeps the viewer focused on key messages while maintaining an engaging loop suited for social media.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"next-project-nav mt-4\">\n    <div class=\"container text-center\">\n      <p class=\"label\">[CONTINUE]</p>\n      <a href=\"work.html\" class=\"mega-title hover-accent\">Next Project <svg width=\"40\" heigh